      <div class="feeling-card stuck">
        <h3>Stuck</h3>
        <p>"Whenever I start I get excited for a day then I'm like nooope, tomorrow!"</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feeling-card lost">
        <h3>Lost</h3>
        <p>"I have trouble even STARTING to workout; I don't know what to do."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feeling-card watched">
        <h3>Watched</h3>
        <p>"I feel like everyone is watching me do it wrong."</p>
        <div class="watched-highlight">GYM INTIMIDATION IS REAL. WE ELIMINATE IT COMPLETELY.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="feelings-subtitle">
