        <p>
          Most people fail because their plan doesn’t fit their real life.
          CBM coaching adapts your training and nutrition around your energy,
          stress, schedule, and goals so you can actually stay consistent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-box">
        <h3>Enjoyment Creates Results</h3>
        <p>
          If you hate your plan, you won’t stick to it.
          That’s why every program is built to help you enjoy training,
          build confidence, and make progress without burnout.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-box">
        <h3>Real Coaching. No BS.</h3>
        <p>
          From fat loss and bodybuilding to performance and lifestyle habits,
          you get direct guidance, accountability, and support that actually
          helps you become better long term.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

